<div class="phototagleft">
</div>
</div>
<p style="margin-bottom:16px"><strong><a href="https://israelwriterstudio.com/">Jennifer Lang</a></strong> (<a href="https://www.instagram.com/jenlangwrites/">@JenLangWrites</a>) is a San Francisco Bay Area transplant in Tel Aviv. Her books include <em><a href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/www.goodreads.com/book/show/142425302-places-we-left-behind__;!!GNU8KkXDZlD12Q!7mN_WlGfk6fz7nT3crcYy64kYgqAbOC4h6YhBG-qses6ngzb1DYF4Bfywt5d42bpHExdMPykKxEwJiQYx1jy1A$" target="_blank" title="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/142425302-places-we-left-behind__;!!GNU8KkXDZlD12Q!7mN_WlGfk6fz7nT3crcYy64kYgqAbOC4h6YhBG-qses6ngzb1DYF4Bfywt5d42bpHExdMPykKxEwJiQYx1jy1A$">Places We Left Behind: A Memoir-in-Miniature</a></em> (2023) and <em><a href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/vineleavespress.myshopify.com/products/landed-a-yogi-s-memoir-in-pieces-poses-by-jennifer-lang?_pos=1&amp;_sid=ab4a08b36&amp;_ss=r__;!!GNU8KkXDZlD12Q!7mN_WlGfk6fz7nT3crcYy64kYgqAbOC4h6YhBG-qses6ngzb1DYF4Bfywt5d42bpHExdMPykKxEwJiR0qQx2Vg$" target="_blank" title="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https://vineleavespress.myshopify.com/products/landed-a-yogi-s-memoir-in-pieces-poses-by-jennifer-lang?_pos=1&amp;_sid=ab4a08b36&amp;_ss=r__;!!GNU8KkXDZlD12Q!7mN_WlGfk6fz7nT3crcYy64kYgqAbOC4h6YhBG-qses6ngzb1DYF4Bfywt5d42bpHExdMPykKxEwJ">Landed: A Yogi’s Memoir in Pieces and Poses</a></em> (2024). Both books are unconventional, very Jewish, Israel-centric, and true. A graduate of Vermont College of Fine Arts, Jennifer was an Assistant Editor at Brevity Journal for years.</p>
<div class="clear"></div>
